headline: Thermo Fisher Scientific Introduces New Laboratory Developed Test to Help Transplant Patients Receive the Right Dose of Critical Anti-Rejection Medication Sooner
summary: WEST HILLS, Calif., February 26, 2026--Thermo Fisher Scientific, the world leader in serving science, today announced the launch of the TacroType™ Pharmacogenetic Test, a new laboratory developed test designed to help inform clinicians on dosing tacrolimus, a commonly prescribed immunosuppressive drug for transplant recipients to lower the risk of rejection.
